+# PR-214 Review Remediation Report
+
+## Thread Triage
+
+- `T-214-01`: actionable
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete outdated-hunk suggestion
+- `T-214-04`: actionable
+- `T-214-05`: actionable
+
+## Changes Applied
+
+- Updated `src/policy/approval_router.py` to normalize the incoming approval state before delegating to the preview payload builder.
+- Updated `src/policy/preview.py` so the fallback payload preserves `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` instead of dropping them when `preview_enabled=False`.
+- Updated `tests/test_preview.py` with regression coverage for the fallback path, including the `manual_review` to `human_review_required` normalization case.
+- Updated `docs/approval_policy.md` so the documented fallback payload matches the corrected runtime behavior.
+
+## Verified Behavior
+
+`build_policy_preview(request_id="req-214", approval_state="manual_review", preview_enabled=False, actor="review-bot")` now returns a payload that keeps:
+
+- `approval_state="human_review_required"`
+- `requires_human_review=true`
+- `status="preview_unavailable"`
+
+## Focused Verification
+
+Executed:
+
+```bash
+python -m unittest tests.test_preview
+python -m unittest tests.test_approval_router
+```
+
+Both test modules passed.
